      "role": "user",
      "content": "honestly i dont even know why im still trying. the last three months have just been a disaster. my lab results were inconclusive, my advisor basically stopped responding to my emails, and now they're saying the grant isn't going through. i feel like i've spent my whole life building this one thing and it's just... crumbling. i'm just so incredibly tired of fighting for something that clearly doesn't want me.",
